'''叙利亚武装部隊'''是[[叙利亚|叙利亚]]的[[军事部队|军事部队]]，包括陆军、海军、空军和防空部队。

==军力==
 
[[叙利亚总统|叙利亚总统]]是叙利亚军队的統帥，包括动员后的总数为646,500的部队。男性满18岁即應召入伍。<ref name="globalsecurity">{{Cite web |url=http://www.globalsecurity.org/military/world/syria/overview.htm |title=Syria - Overview |accessdate=2012-01-30 |archive-date=2012-01-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120119050144/http://www.globalsecurity.org/military/world/syria/overview.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>义务兵役时间在逐年降低，2005年从两年半降为两年，2008年降至21个月，2011年降到一年半。<ref>[http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/xinhua/2011-03-20/content_2068776.html Syria reduces compulsory military service by three months] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110503190742/http://www.chinadaily.com.cn/xinhua/2011-03-20/content_2068776.html |date=2011-05-03 }}</ref>大约2万名叙利亚士兵被部署在[[黎巴嫩|黎巴嫩]]。2005年4月27日，最后一支叙利亚军队离开驻军了30年的黎巴嫩。<ref name="globalsecurity"/>

叙利亚军力在[[阿拉伯世界|阿拉伯世界]]排名第三，仅次于[[埃及|埃及]]和[[伊拉克|伊拉克]]。2011年内战后，由於陣亡、變節、拒服兵役等，曾經擁有30萬兵力的敘利亞政府軍已經萎縮近半。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world/2015/07/150726_assad_syria_army |title=阿薩德罕見承認敘利亞政府軍兵力匱乏 |publisher=BBC |date=2015-07-26 |language=zh-hant |accessdate=2015-08-04 |archive-date=2015-07-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150730074219/http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/trad/world/2015/07/150726_assad_syria_army |dead-url=no }}</ref>

== 组成 ==
大多常规职业士兵属于[[阿萨德家族|阿萨德家族]]所属的[[阿拉维派|阿拉维派]]。阿拉维派仅占该国人口的12%，不过却占军队总数的98%<ref name=Bhalla>{{cite web|last=Bhalla|first=Reva|title=Making Sense of the Syrian Crisis|url=http://www.stratfor.com/weekly/20110504-making-sense-syrian-crisis?utm_source=GWeekly&utm_medium=email&utm_campaign=110505&utm_content=readmore&elq=2ef73758a9434404bd465acd3490d5fe#ixzz1LTPFUuuw|publisher=Stratfor Global Intelligence|accessdate=9 May 2011|archive-date=2011-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111120165103/http://www.stratfor.com/weekly/20110504-making-sense-syrian-crisis?utm_source=GWeekly&utm_medium=email&utm_campaign=110505&utm_content=readmore&elq=2ef73758a9434404bd465acd3490d5fe#ixzz1LTPFUuuw|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=State>{{cite web|title=Background Note: Syria|url=http://www.state.gov/r/pa/ei/bgn/3580.htm|publisher=US State Department|accessdate=14 September 2011|archive-date=2015-06-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150613073738/http://www.state.gov/r/pa/ei/bgn/3580.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。20万正规职业军人中有14万是阿拉维派人士<ref>{{cite news|last=Marshall|first=Tim|title=Why Syria's Regime Is Still Holding Out|url=http://news.sky.com/skynews/Home/World-News/Sky-News-Analysis-Tim-Marshall-Looks-At-Why-The-Bashir-Al-Assad-Regime-Has-Not-Collapsed/Article/201105115987446?lpos=World_News_First_Home_Page_Feature_Teaser_Region_0&lid=ARTICLE_15987446_Sky_News_Analysis%3A_Tim_Marshall_Looks_At_Why_The_Bashir_Al_Assad_Regime_Has_Not_Collapsed_|accessdate=9 May 2011|newspaper=Sky News|date=7 May 2011|archive-date=2021-03-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210304112548/https://news.sky.com/?lpos=World_News_First_Home_Page_Feature_Teaser_Region_0&lid=ARTICLE_15987446_Sky_News_Analysis%3A_Tim_Marshall_Looks_At_Why_The_Bashir_Al_Assad_Regime_Has_Not_Collapsed_|dead-url=no}}</ref>，而部队的指挥官中的95%都是阿拉维派。

不过在应召入伍的30万士兵中，以及叙利亚[[空军|空军]]驾驶员中则有很多[[逊尼派|逊尼派]]<ref name="Bhalla"/><ref>{{cite news|title=Syria's military: what does Assad have?|url=http://af.reuters.com/article/libyaNews/idAFLDE72S19O20110406|work=Reuters|accessdate=5 May 2011|date=6 April 2011|archive-date=2011-07-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110718003308/http://af.reuters.com/article/libyaNews/idAFLDE72S19O20110406|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
