=== 供应 ===
[[苏联解体|苏联解体]]导致长期依靠苏联提供训练、装备和贷款支持的叙军队减缓了军事现代化发展速度。1990年代早期，射程500公里的[[飛毛腿飛彈|Scud-C]]导弹买自[[朝鲜|朝鲜]]，射程700公里的Scud-D据报道是在朝鲜和[[伊朗|伊朗]]的帮助下本国生产的<ref>[http://www.theglobeandmail.com/servlet/Page/document/v4/sub/MarketingPage?user_URL=http://www.theglobeandmail.com%2Fservlet%2FArticleNews%2FTPStory%2FLAC%2F20040928%2FCOSYRIA28%2FTPComment%2FTopStories&ord=2674524&brand=theglobeandmail&redirect_reason=2&denial_reasons=none&force_login=false "Syria's embrace of WMD"] {{Wayback|url=http://www.theglobeandmail.com/servlet/Page/document/v4/sub/MarketingPage?user_URL=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.theglobeandmail.com%2Fservlet%2FArticleNews%2FTPStory%2FLAC%2F20040928%2FCOSYRIA28%2FTPComment%2FTopStories&ord=2674524&brand=theglobeandmail&redirect_reason=2&denial_reasons=none&force_login=false |date=20090116184238 }} by Eyal Zisser, ''Globe and Mail'', September 28, 2004 (link leads only to abstract; purchase necessary for full article)</ref>。 

由于叙参加了[[海湾战争|海湾战争]]，因此叙利亚得到了来自于海湾国家的资金支援，这些钱主要用做[[军费|军费]]开支。2005年，[[俄罗斯|俄罗斯]]免除了叙四分之三的军费欠款，即大约134亿美元中的98亿，这些贷款主要是在苏联时代遗留下来的。俄方这样做的目的是要与叙签署新的武器购销合同<ref name=GlobalSecurity>{{cite book|last=Weitz|first=Richard|title=Global security watch--Russia : a reference handbook|year=2010|publisher=Praeger Security International|location=Santa Barbara, Calif.|isbn=9780313354342|pages=30|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=VcdZ9s2IAwMC&pg=PA30&dq=russian+navy+syria+tartous#v=onepage&q&f=false|access-date=2012-02-01|archive-date=2014-01-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140111222622/http://books.google.com/books?id=VcdZ9s2IAwMC&pg=PA30&dq=russian+navy+syria+tartous#v=onepage&q&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2011年，俄罗斯作为叙利亚最大的武器供应商，当年叙花费了至少40亿美元从俄进口武器<ref name=SIPRI/><ref name=Amos>{{cite news|last=Amos|first=Howard|title=News Analysis: Russia Damages Image in Arab Spring|url=http://www.themoscowtimes.com/business/article/news-analysis-russia-damages-image-in-arab-spring/442712.html|accessdate=8 September 2011|newspaper=The Moscow Times|date=26 August 2011|archive-date=2011-12-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111222175458/http://www.themoscowtimes.com/business/article/news-analysis-russia-damages-image-in-arab-spring/442712.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=CAST>{{cite web|title=Russian defense industry and arms trade:  facts and figures|url=http://www.cast.ru/files/2011/all-stats_eng_2011_05_12.pdf|publisher=Centre for Analysis of Strategies and Technologies. pp 15|accessdate=8 September 2011|archive-date=2011-11-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111120172100/http://www.cast.ru/files/2011/all-stats_eng_2011_05_12.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=Meyer>{{cite news|last=Meyer|first=Henry|title=<nowiki>Assad Ouster Bid May Unleash ‘Chaos in Mideast,’ Russia Says</nowiki>|url=http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-07/assad-ouster-bid-may-unleash-chaos-in-mideast-russia-says.html|accessdate=8 September 2011|newspaper=Bloomberg|date=7 September 2011|archive-date=2012-04-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120427145004/http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-07/assad-ouster-bid-may-unleash-chaos-in-mideast-russia-says.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

叙利亚更是俄制武器在[[中东|中东]]地区的最大进口国<ref>{{cite web |url=http://war.163.com/12/0210/14/7PTJLI1100011MTO.html |language= |title=叙利亚欠俄134亿美元 或再签20亿军售订单 |publisher=环球时报 |date=2012-02-10 |accessdate= |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120213173419/http://war.163.com/12/0210/14/7PTJLI1100011MTO.html |archive-date=2012-02-13 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。此外，[[伊朗|伊朗]]与叙利亚在2006年签订了联合防务协定<ref>{{cite web |url=http://cn.reuters.com/article/CNTopGenNews/idCNCNE88204320120903 |language= |title=伊朗军官：若叙利亚遭美国袭击 伊朗将采取行动 |publisher=路透社 |date=2012年9月3日 |accessdate= |archive-date=2012年9月5日 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120905130033/http://cn.reuters.com/article/CNTopGenNews/idCNCNE88204320120903 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

从2011年开始的[[叙利亚内战|叙利亚内战]]中，[[伊朗|伊朗]]和[[俄罗斯|俄罗斯]]继续为叙当局输送武器，伊朗也因此违反了[[联合国|联合国]]禁止其出口武器的规定<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.zaobao.com/special/hotspot/pages2/hotspot120305.shtml |language= |title=伊朗助叙加强镇压反对派 |publisher=联合早报 |date=2012-03-05 |accessdate= |archive-date=2012-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120305104636/http://www.zaobao.com/special/hotspot/pages2/hotspot120305.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://war.163.com/12/0701/14/85B6G7K700011MTO.html |language= |title=联合国报告称伊朗违反规定向叙利亚输送武器 |publisher=新华网 |date=2012-07-01 |accessdate= |archive-date=2012-07-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120704091054/http://war.163.com/12/0701/14/85B6G7K700011MTO.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.scotsman.com/news/international/syria-moscow-sends-navy-vessels-to-syrian-port-1-2362099 |title=Syria: Moscow sends navy vessels to Syrian port |accessdate=2012-07-01 |archive-date=2020-04-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200427003625/https://www.scotsman.com/news/world/syria-moscow-sends-navy-vessels-syrian-port-2468187 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。内战中有不少当局高官变节加入反对派，如陆军后勤部门参谋长卡勒夫将军等。<ref >{{cite web|url=http://www.zaobao.com/gj/gj130318_009.shtml | language= | title=叙利亚将军变节投奔约旦 |publisher=联合早报 |date=2013-03-18 |accessdate= }}</ref>

